---
// src/components/CommunityIndex.astro
---
 
<!-- Page hero -->
<div class="section-dark pt-28 sm:pt-36 pb-16 sm:pb-20 text-center px-5 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(251,191,36,0.10) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
  <div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-5">
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
      <span class="font-body text-amber-500 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Beyond the Dance Floor</span>
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
    </div>
    <span class="gold-line mx-auto"></span>
    <h1 class="section-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl text-white mb-6">
      Siyakhathalela.<br/>
      <span class="text-amber-400">We Care.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
      eKoneni isn't just where Mdantsane grooves — it's where Mdantsane looks after its own.
      Every story here is proof that a business can be more than a business.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
<!-- Stories -->
<section class="section-mid py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
 
    <!-- Featured — House Rebuild -->
    <a href="/community/house-rebuild" class="group block community-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-8 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-amber-400">
      <div class="h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-amber-600"></div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 min-h-[400px]">
 
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[260px] lg:min-h-0">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 text-center">
            <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-amber-400/20 mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/30 text-sm">Replace with cover photo</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Uncomment when photo is ready:
          <img
            src="/images/community/house-rebuild-cover.jpg"
            alt="eKoneni rebuilds a family home"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
          />
          -->
          <div class="absolute top-5 left-5 z-10">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-400 rounded-full font-body text-black text-xs font-bold tracking-wide">
              ● Latest
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <div class="p-8 sm:p-12 flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 font-body text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-5">
              House Rebuild · 2025
            </span>
            <h2 class="section-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-5 group-hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors duration-300">
              A Family Lost Everything.<br/>
              <span class="text-amber-400">eKoneni Built It Back.</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed">
              Fire destroyed a family's home in Mdantsane last week. A mother and her children lost everything.
              eKoneni arrived with materials, tools, and people. Roofing done. Painting done. Electricity next.
              The job isn't finished until that family is truly home.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-amber-400/10">
            <span class="font-body text-amber-400 text-sm font-medium">Read the full story</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
 
      </div>
    </a>
 
    <!-- Smaller — Feeding Scheme -->
    <a href="/community/feeding-scheme" class="group block community-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-amber-400">
      <div class="h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-amber-400"></div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] min-h-[200px]">
 
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[200px] sm:min-h-0">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-amber-400/20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <!-- Uncomment when photo is ready:
          <img
            src="/images/community/feeding-scheme-cover.jpg"
            alt="eKoneni feeding children in Mdantsane"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
          />
          -->
        </div>
 
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 font-body text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">
            Feeding Scheme · 2024
          </span>
          <h2 class="section-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-amber-300 transition-colors duration-300">
            Two Weeks. Every Child Fed.
          </h2>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">
            No conditions. No press releases. Just meals on the table for children in Mdantsane,
            every single day for two weeks straight. This is what eKoneni means by community.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="font-body text-amber-400 text-sm font-medium">Read the full story</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
 
      </div>
    </a>
 
  </div>
</section>
